Shakhtar come into the Champions League match short of competitive action with the Ukrainian Premier League still on a winter break, and have had to rely upon friendlies in Spain and Brazil to stay sharp.

Bayern Munich are cruising at the top of Bundesliga and thrashed Hamburg 8-0 at the weekend however there is some hope for the hosts.

Shakhtar have the leading goalscorer in this season’s Champions League, Luiz Adriano, in their side. Who has scored nine goals from only 10 shots on target in the Champions League this season.

